the secret of &lt;unk&gt; is a 2013 animated adventure film written and directed by &lt;unk&gt; moore and based on the novel of the same name by irish author arthur mythology . the film stars brendan gleeson as the title character . the film premiered at the annecy international animated film festival . the film was selected as the irish entry for the best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but it did not make the final shortlist . the film was selected as the irish entry for the best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but was not nominated .